#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.97"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.97:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.97:0.2"
msgid "9. Gaṅgāpeyyālavagga"
msgstr "9. Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.97:0.3"
msgid "97. Paṭhamasamuddaninnasutta"
msgstr "97. Slanting to the Ocean"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.97:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gaṅgā nadī samuddaninnā samuddapoṇā samuddapabbhārā;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, the Ganges river slants, slopes, and inclines to the ocean."

msgctxt "sn45.97:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who develops the noble eightfold path slants, "
"slopes, and inclines to extinguishment. …”"

msgctxt "sn45.97:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.97:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe … "
"sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.97:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.97:1.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
